          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NRC Office of Public Engagement and Participation Act of 2023&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill establishes an independent office within the Nuclear Regulatory Commission (NRC) to advocate for the public within NRC jurisdiction and support public participation in NRC proceedings and activities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
